<inglise> Whereas the establishment of sampling procedures and of the methods of analysis required for checking the substances listed and their purity standards constitute technical implementing measures; whereas in order to simplify and expedite these procedures and facilitate their application it is desirable to ensure close cooperation between the Member States and the Commission within the Standing Committee for Foodstuffs set up by Council Decision 69/414/EEC (1), </inglise>
